### 11. Top K elements — multiple approaches

**Question:** Find top K largest in stream of unknown length.

**Answer:** Min-heap size K O(n log k); quickselect O(n) average; bucket sort if range bounded.

**Difficulty Level:** Hard

**Interview Tips:** Compare when n vs k dominates; distributed partial heaps merge.

